      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/4952.John_Berendt">About John Berendt</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/4952.John_Berendt"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1204661056p3/4952.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/4952.John_Berendt">John Berendt
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
785
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10390357702012896004">The son of two writers, John Berendt grew up in Syracuse, New York. He earned a B.A. in English from Harvard University, where he worked on the staff of <i>The Harvard Lampoon</i>. After graduating in 1961, he moved to New York City to pursue a career in publishing. He was editor of <i>New York</i> magazine from 1977 to 1979, and wrote a monthly column for <i>Esquire</i> from 1982 to 1994.<br/><br/>Berendt first traveled to Sav</span>
  <span id="freeText10390357702012896004" style="display:none">The son of two writers, John Berendt grew up in Syracuse, New York. He earned a B.A. in English from Harvard University, where he worked on the staff of <i>The Harvard Lampoon</i>. After graduating in 1961, he moved to New York City to pursue a career in publishing. He was editor of <i>New York</i> magazine from 1977 to 1979, and wrote a monthly column for <i>Esquire</i> from 1982 to 1994.<br /><br />Berendt first traveled to Savannah in the early 80's, and spent more and more time there over the next few years, until he was there more often than he was in New York.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10390357702012896004" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

