      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/300461-midnight-in-the-garden-of-good-and-evil">Quotes from Midnight in the G...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
